ding":"1","heading_align":"t4s-text-center","top_heading":"","icon_heading":"las la-gem","top_subheading":"","tophead_mb":30,"accor_des":"1","title_cl":"#222222","bg_title_cl":"#f6f6f8","title_active_cl":"#000000","bg_title_active_cl":"#f6f6f8","content_cl":"#878787","bg_content_cl":"#ffffff","content_align":"t4s-text-start","auto_active":false,"layout":"t4s-container-wrap","custom_width":1000,"cl_bg":"","cl_bg_gradient":"","mg":",,50px,","pd":"","mg_tb":"","pd_tb":"","mg_mb":",,30px,","pd_mb":"","use_cus_css":false,"code_cus_css":""}},"1737356109e0ff6ec8":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"judge_me_reviews_review_widget_rQyQa3":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/judge-me-reviews\/blocks\/review_widget\/61ccd3b1-a9f2-4160-9fe9-4fec8413e5d8","settings":{}}},"block_order":["judge_me_reviews_review_widget_rQyQa3"],"settings":{}},"83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0":{"type":"accordion","blocks":{"template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-1":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Is NG EarSafe Comm Waterproof?","content":"<p>No, These are water & sweatproof open ear headphones with noise-canceling mic that are perfect for workouts, outdoor activities, or rainy days. NG EarSafe Comm is designed for durability with an IPx5 rating.<\/p>"}},"template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-2":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":" Is NG EarSafe Compatible with iPhone as well as Android?","content":"<p>Yes, NG EarSafe Comm is compatible with both iPhone and Android devices. These Bluetooth headphones with a noise-canceling mic can seamlessly connect to any device that supports Bluetooth, making them ideal for work meetings or online classes.<\/p>"}},"template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-3":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Can anyone hear your calls & music?","content":"<p>No, the advanced anti-leakage technology in these open-ear headphones, combined with a noise-canceling mic, effectively reduces sound leakage, ensuring privacy for your calls and music. However, like any other headphones, if the volume is turned up too high in a very quiet environment, some sound may still be faintly heard outside.<\/p>"}},"d3cd347d-e340-4be5-8075-724fb61f46c9":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Is it lightweight & comfortable?","content":"<p>Yes, NG EarSafe Comm is incredibly lightweight at just 29 grams. The open ear design for all-day wear ensures comfort during work meetings, <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/blogs\/open-ear-headphones\/5-major-benefits-of-cycling\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">cycling<\/span><\/a>, or long video calls.<\/p>"}},"c8df18a8-c3a3-47ba-a1d0-511389dc6c2b":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Can we attend online meetings with NG EarSafe Comm?","content":"<p>Yes, these open ear headphones with noise-canceling mic are perfect for <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/blogs\/open-ear-headphones\/best-noise-canceling-headset-for-working-from-home\" title=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/blogs\/open-ear-headphones\/best-noise-canceling-headset-for-working-from-home\">online meetings<\/a>. The adjustable boom mic filters ambient sound and delivers crystal-clear voice quality, making them one of the best choices for remote work or virtual classes.<\/p>"}},"cb9f90a1-53a4-4f3a-bb30-97cc923f8403":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Can the Boom Microphone be detached?","content":"<p>No, the boom microphone cannot be removed. However, it is fully adjustable and designed with noise isolation to provide clear audio, even during outdoor calls or in noisy surroundings.<\/p>"}},"f8a2580d-f121-491c-8d46-eaa29c7acdac":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Can NG EarSafe be connected with 2 devices at the same time?","content":"<p>NG EarSafe Comm supports dual pairing, allowing you to connect to two devices simultaneously. With its fast Bluetooth pairing, you can work, listen, and switch easily. seamlessly transitioning between meetings and calls without hassle.<\/p>"}},"03f7bb3f-1225-459e-9f76-2ca5a55631b8":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"What is the warranty period?","content":"<p>We offer a 1-year replacement warranty for NG EarSafe Comm, covering all manufacturing defects. This warranty applies to the full range of our open ear wireless headphones with noise-canceling mic (Physical or water damage is not covered.)<\/p>"}},"63221feb-cd8f-4fb9-b052-2210cdd73abf":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"What if I don’t like the product?","content":"<p>We offer an easy 7-day return policy for NG EarSafe Comm. If you’re not satisfied with these open ear headphones with mic, <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/pages\/return-exchange\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">you can return them<\/span><\/a> within 7 days of delivery. Note that products with physical damage will not be accepted.<\/p>"}},"ee28a4f7-8a1c-49dd-9d22-eeeef249d3cd":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"The prepaid offer of ₹200 off is valid on which mode of payment?","content":"<p>Enjoy a flat ₹200 instant discount on payment using any Credit\/Debit cards or UPI. This offer applies to the entire range, including lightweight open ear headphones with noise-canceling mic.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-1","template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-2","template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-3","d3cd347d-e340-4be5-8075-724fb61f46c9","c8df18a8-c3a3-47ba-a1d0-511389dc6c2b","cb9f90a1-53a4-4f3a-bb30-97cc923f8403","f8a2580d-f121-491c-8d46-eaa29c7acdac","03f7bb3f-1225-459e-9f76-2ca5a55631b8","63221feb-cd8f-4fb9-b052-2210cdd73abf","ee28a4f7-8a1c-49dd-9d22-eeeef249d3cd"],"settings":{"design_heading":"1","heading_align":"t4s-text-center